name: ADUserDuplicates_DuplicateUsersByID
query:
SELECT employeeID, givenName, sn, sAMAccountName, mail, userPrincipalName
FROM f_App_ADUserDuplicates_List_Users
WHERE employeeID IN (
  SELECT employeeID
  FROM f_App_ADUserDuplicates_List_Users
  WHERE length(employeeID) > 0
  GROUP BY employeeID
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
  )
ORDER BY employeeID
